service

Class Population<PersonType extends Person>

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.Population<PersonType>

  •  class Population<PersonType extends Person>
extends java.lang.Object
    A Binary Search Tree that holds nodes that are children of the Person object. More efficient search than a linear algorithm in most cases.

    Bugs: empty BST will raise errors with search

    Author:
    Andi Gu

      • compare

        private int compare(PersonType a,
          PersonType b)
        Helper function that compares two people.
        Parameters:
        a - The first person to be compared.
        b - The second person to be compared.
        Returns:
        A negative number of a's username is less lexicographically than b's, zero if they're the same and a positive number if a's username is greater lexicographically than b's.
